---
// src/components/Footer.astro
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="w-full bg-black text-gray-400 py-8 mt-auto border-t border-gray-800">
	<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-3 text-sm">
		
		<p class="text-gray-300 font-semibold">
			&copy; {currentYear} AO Loot Logs Comparator
		</p>
		
		<p class="max-w-2xl">
			Built for Albion Online guilds to automate loot analysis. Compares exported 
			<span class="text-gray-300">aostatistics</span> logs against shared chest logs to verify direct deposits.
		</p>

		<p class="text-xs text-gray-500">
			Powered by Google Sheets & GitHub Pages. <br />
			This tool is an independent, open-source project and is not affiliated with or endorsed by Sandbox Interactive GmbH.
		</p>

		<div class="flex gap-6 mt-2 text-sm">
			<a 
				href="https://github.com/your-username/your-repo-name" 
				target="_blank" 
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
				class="hover:text-white transition-colors"
			>
				Source Code
			</a>
			<a 
				href="https://matheus.sampaio.us/ao-loot-logger-viewer/" 
				target="_blank" 
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
				class="hover:text-white transition-colors"
			>
				Inspiration
			</a>
		</div>

	</div>
</footer>